  "commentary": "Contextual CxT and the static xT surface rank players similarly overall (Spearman 0.88), but they disagree sharply on individuals. Jo\u00e3o Filipe Iria Santos Moutinho rises 327 places under contextual CxT (xT rank 520 -> 193): the model credits the build-up context of their actions, not just the pitch zone. Conversely Boualem Khoukhi falls 302 places (xT rank 304 -> 606): high touch volume in nominally valuable zones, but low contextual threat. The biggest fallers are typically goalkeepers and defenders the static surface overrates. Whom you shortlist as a threat-creator changes for the movers, which is the point of a contextual metric.",
